# SQL Functions and Data Transformation Project

## Project Overview

This project contains SQL solutions to a set of practical business and data transformation exercises. The tasks focus on data extraction, formatting, calculations, conditional logic, and analytical reporting using SQL.

## Skills Demonstrated

- String Functions
- Date Functions
- CASE Statements
- Calculated Columns
- Data Formatting
- Data Filtering
- Concatenation
- Business Query Development
- Data Transformation

## Tasks Completed

### Q1
Extract first name and surname from customer names.

### Q2
Identify customers born between midnight and 6 AM.

### Q3
Retrieve products marked as returned.

### Q4
Format sales dates and create a Month_Year field.

### Q5
Calculate adjusted sales values based on return status.

### Q6
Compute profit/loss using adjusted sales values.

### Q7
Determine order quarters from order dates.

### Q8
Extract and concatenate product names with initials.

### Q9
Identify products with costs greater than 9000.

